        c. ptcp. aor. (cl), Lk 23:9. 
      Seq. εἰς (cf. Heb. הָיָה לְ), a vernac. usage (M, Pr., 71): Mt 19:5, Mk 10:8, He 8:10, al.  
      C. adv.: Mt 19:20, Mk 4:26, Lk 18:11, al.  
